    public class BaseAclfBusImpl<TGen extends AclfGen,TLoad extends AclfLoad>
extends BusImpl
implements BaseAclfBus<TGen,TLoad>
    An implementation of the model object 'Bus'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Gen Code
    • Load Code
    • Voltage Mag
    • Voltage Ang
    • Desired Volt Mag
    • Desired Volt Ang
    • Gen P
    • Gen Q
    • Load P
    • Load Q
    • Shunt Y
    • Exp Load P
    • Exp Load Q
    • QGen Limit
    • PGen Limit
    • VLimit
    • External Power Into Net
    • Contribute Gen List
    • Contribute Load List
    • Compensator List
    • Switched Shunt List
    • Function Load
    • Bus Control
    • Remote QControl Group
